  "title": "FMCG QA Executive | Up to $4k + Benefits | Near Tai Seng MRT",
  "description": "<p><strong>💰 Salary</strong></p><p>✔️ <strong>Up to $4k/month</strong></p><p><strong>📍 Location</strong></p><p>✔️<strong> Near Tai Seng MRT</strong></p><p>✔️ Accessible and well-connected workplace</p><p><strong>🎯 Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Oversee overall food <strong>quality and safety</strong> at Central Kitchen</li><li>Ensure products meet company and regulatory standards</li><li>Develop, review, and enhance QA policies</li><li>Conduct regular <strong>inspections, audits, and compliance checks</strong></li><li>Maintain and improve quality control procedures</li><li>Investigate customer feedback and conduct root-cause analysis</li><li>Verify compliance with QA  protocols and SOPs</li><li>Monitor product quality standards consistently</li><li>Ensure adherence to <strong>HACCP & AVA/NEA guidelines</strong></li><li>Supervise and manage all QA department activities</li><li>Support product & process development</li><li>Assist in <strong>R&D, food tasting, and process improvements</strong></li><li>Any other duties assigned by Chief QA Officer / Manager</li></ul><p><strong>📝 Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Strong background in Food Science, QA, or food manufacturing</li><li>Experience in quality management, audits, and regulatory compliance is advantageous</li><li>Knowledge of HACCP, NEA, and AVA standards</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>📩 <strong>Interested?</strong></p><p>Apply now by sending your <strong>Name, Email Contact No.</strong> to <a href=\"tel:8891%204996\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">8891 4996</a>*.</p><p><br /></p><p>*Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p><br /></p><p>CREW by HRNet | HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd (24C2435)</p><p>Athirah Bte Rosli (R2197227)</p>",
